          .step__content-wrapper 
            .step__content
              h3.step__heading STEP 1: 
                span WeR the Right Fit
              .step__img 
                img(src="img/icon-inquiry.png" alt="inquiry")
              p.step__text Connect with WeR Consultants so we can help you explore your processes to pinpoint what you have, what you need, and what can be improved to determine if we are the right fit. If WeR fits, we will work out an agreement for you to sign before we move on to the next step.
